{"tid":1785842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"poly 廚房送左入精神病房23日！","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:55:51.000Z","uid":128625,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03cc996dcda6a653b8300924f99e405908ae83ff","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"(傳)//緊急！緊急！！！<br />\n我屌晒你地呀，當poly廚房佬係condom。<br />\n<br />\n已經被困左係東區醫院精神病房K4, 23日！<br />\n講多一次，係已經23日！<br />\n一直只可以屋企人，同埋星火律師探病，任何人進入一律搜身，同坐監冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n星期二（聽日），<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就會被醫生落高劑量的抗奮藥物，拒絕食用的話，會直接插喉落藥。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">家人要見醫生反對落藥，醫生話放咗假，所以家人阻止唔到。</span></span><br />\n依家佢好怕變到抑鬱，然後被自殺。<br />\n<br />\n近日事件：<br />\n1. 12/12 佢去沖涼期間，有人放張恐嚇字條係佢本書嗰度。<br />\n<br />\n2. 13/12 佢申請出院，醫生立即決定17/12加重藥，冇得離開。<br />\n<br />\n3. 13/12 下午<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人冒認佢阿媽話要探佢</span></span>，然後佢拒絕見，醫院就落咗一個記錄，「病人唔接見家人，所以屋企人都唔可以探病」。而家佢嘅情況好危險。<br />\n<br />\n4. 搵個蘋果同埋立場幫手，甚至蘋果用電話訪問左一個鐘，但記者覺得冇報道意義。<br />\n<br />\n而家我朋友極度害怕，仲要食亢奮藥，佢好希望大家幫佢手，引起人關注。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知真定假，有無人fact check</span></span>"},{"pid":"31fc132fca62ee1b26ede4e8461b4d2b166411cf","tid":1785842,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於明日主題為哀悼 <br />\n請各位穿黑衫到場以示哀悼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1U75uD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1U75uD.png&h=d951bb19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對社署打壓 我地更要齊心"},{"pid":"4492b93cae6b59d5c9832dcc287a635b4cb0c54d","tid":1785842,"uid":199120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d38a9a2a71a15a1488205fa009cbf3b2cca6be","tid":1785842,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"點緊急都好，個標題唔好有錯先呀，連登太多錯字標題搞到好多人都冇撳入去<br />\n<br />\n幫手推下先"},{"pid":"3a5c7474fd839a5acde4bc30d951f5725b6f79d0","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d38a9a2a71a15a1488205fa009cbf3b2cca6be","tid":1785842,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"點緊急都好，個標題唔好有錯先呀，連登太多錯字標題搞到好多人都冇撳入去<br />\n<br />\n幫手推下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"下次會睇清楚先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31e00951ef4af3be79959d17d14eaf0f747817e","tid":1785842,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a5c7474fd839a5acde4bc30d951f5725b6f79d0","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d38a9a2a71a15a1488205fa009cbf3b2cca6be","tid":1785842,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"點緊急都好，個標題唔好有錯先呀，連登太多錯字標題搞到好多人都冇撳入去<br />\n<br />\n幫手推下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"下次會睇清楚先開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"我諗緊poly廚房出事定廚房佬出事<br />\n<br />\n幫手推"},{"pid":"291cb9bbc5e1ded0dd89473114078d06669c3d3d","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2a8b6fbafe6ef11ed1f3eed26a8b4fa86e9038d0","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"03312ff23b199047205b6060f63ccd75a2f17f1f","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"40d82660530ccba01be281a15f4b06d756c90951","tid":1785842,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ccca475d1b1305c54f9c35352bf64268f6cff22f","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"7f2f53c738e80a1c00a0d158dcfe639d59451fb1","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:01.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"14dad65b2be31cca2b6b8922fddff7a280933129","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"057d4d7432d35d9662c85f9fbb787a423a017968","tid":1785842,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"Push 你個頭 睇左鄭錦滿ig再講野"},{"pid":"5af29ce771c4996aaa3ab12e66ac56756ea833f6","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"f0d80a94e1005b44c81083681d54c09006f3025e","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"f816879a4f5f4b8dee58f71c8526421bb0bd0b3f","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"a569419392916bc914cf891e505138ec22767d8b","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"a67438d4c5bdaa1e505837a9be0f196e9a17a9d7","tid":1785842,"uid":297835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"第四點好撚假喎"},{"pid":"6a5814f5f3a5aabaf855c058c03cc68047566fd6","tid":1785842,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d7b16cb1407c42878a933e7ecebeb906b697704","tid":1785842,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:50:40.000Z","msg":"邊個再psuh邊個就係鬼 睇左鄭錦滿fb再講野"},{"pid":"08de7b4ff8017b455de161f8f586d3da5cf081e8","tid":1785842,"uid":128625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更正</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明白大家好關心廚房佬，我地都係，但希望大家明白幾件事。<br />\n<br />\n第一，經歷Poly件事後，唔少人都會唔開心，或有其他更激烈嘅情緒。醫生係按廚房佬當時嘅情緒狀況，而決定安排佢入院接受治療。如果由得佢唔理嘅話，廚房佬情緒狀況可能會更差。<br />\n<br />\n第二，用藥其實係為廚房佬好。當佢常期處於亢奮狀態，休息唔到，個人其實會好攰。藥物係想令佢舒服d，休息得好至能康復。當然，每種藥物都會有其副作用，點控制，依方面我地交返俾精神科嘅同事。(請相信該病房嘅手足，佢地好黃的) <br />\n<br />\n第三，廚房佬處於咁亢奮嘅狀態，純對話輔導等等係幫唔到佢。拒絕用藥，只會令個情況更差，所以至需要插胃喉落藥以繼續療程。(Psy ward普遍用po，唔用IV / IM)<br />\n<br />\n第四，負責醫生放左假，替假嘅醫生係唔會見家人。<br />\n<br />\n第五，暫時唔俾廚房佬見其他人，都係希望廚房佬可以免受其他刺激，靜靜地康復。<br />\n<br />\n第六，可唔可以回家渡假係按病情而定。如果廚房佬情緒唔穩定，醫護點會放心俾佢離開醫院。 24日對於精神科治療黎講，其實唔算長，有d可以以月計。心靈上受創同普通傷風感冒唔同，係需要較長時間嘅治療。<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家相信醫院嘅手足，並俾d時間同空間俾善良嘅廚房佬，祝願佢早日康復。‼️唔好再瘋傳佢全名啦‼<br />\n️<br />\n#Poly廚房佬 update!!!<br />\n<br />\nFrom tg : Polyu哨兵"}]}